By the way, a brick is
a dangerous instrument

19:56.133 --> 19:58.467
and if you followed him
out into a public street

19:58.533 --> 20:01.100
with a dangerous instrument,
that's a no-no,

20:01.166 --> 20:02.700
-do you understand?
-Yes, ma'am.

20:02.767 --> 20:04.667
It's not a dangerous instrument

20:04.734 --> 20:06.066
if you build a building with it,

20:06.133 --> 20:09.767
