or if you throw it at them,

20:09.834 --> 20:11.967
it's a dangerous instrument,
do you understand?

20:12.033 --> 20:13.000
Yes.

20:13.066 --> 20:15.967
Now I want you to tell me
your version of what he,

20:16.033 --> 20:18.834
so you went there,
he had blocked you from Instagram,

20:18.900 --> 20:22.900
so that you know that
for some ungodly reason,

20:22.967 --> 20:25.433
he's blocked you,
he's cut you off,

20:25.500 --> 20:27.266
you never had any
problem with him before.

20:27.333 --> 20:29.567
So you go to his house
with a driver.

20:29.633 --> 20:30.667
Correct.

20:30.734 --> 20:33.300
One o'clock in the
afternoon unannounced.

20:33.367 --> 20:34.467
That's correct, Your Honor.

20:34.533 --> 20:36.100
And you go into the backyard?

