20:37.834 --> 20:39.200
I'm walking to the side gate

20:39.266 --> 20:40.333
and his parents live separately,

20:40.400 --> 20:41.834
they live on one
side of the house

20:41.900 --> 20:43.567
and he lives on the other
side of the house, right?

20:43.633 --> 20:45.300
