[Brandon] Yes, I smell marijuana.

20:55.667 --> 20:56.967
-From the back?
-Yes.

20:57.033 --> 20:58.700
Well, from his front of the yard,

20:58.767 --> 21:01.467
-it's his front of the yard.
-Okay. Okay, keep going.

21:01.533 --> 21:03.300
Like I said, I'm walking
to the front gate.

