21:55.734 --> 21:59.066
I was not 10 feet inside, I was--
my back was towards the gate

21:59.133 --> 22:01.033
and as I reacted
and I punched him--

22:01.100 --> 22:02.700
-What was being said?
-What was said?

22:02.967 --> 22:04.900
He was telling me to
"Get the... out of here,"

22:04.967 --> 22:07.066
