25:42.266 --> 25:44.600
and he wasn't somebody
who had done anything to you,

25:44.667 --> 25:47.900
except that you took some
bad advice from Steve.

25:47.967 --> 25:49.467
Your Honor, he trespassed.

25:49.533 --> 25:53.033
He was told to leave multiple
times by my wife as well.

25:53.100 --> 25:54.834
