25:57.800 --> 25:58.800
No, Your Honor.

25:58.867 --> 26:01.934
I'm not excusing coming
to your house unannounced.

26:02.000 --> 26:03.934
What I'm saying is
that you were high,

26:04.000 --> 26:06.967
you had taken bad advice,
you took his property

26:07.033 --> 26:08.400
