26:08.467 --> 26:09.667
He came to get his property,

26:09.734 --> 26:12.667
which he probably shouldn't
have done unannounced,

26:12.734 --> 26:14.166
'cause he knew that
there would be trouble,

26:14.233 --> 26:17.600
but you don't see any
complicity on your part?

26:17.667 --> 26:20.467
Yes, I understand
that I messed up on--

26:20.533 --> 26:22.100
-On a lot of things.
-On ignoring his message.

26:22.166 --> 26:23.867
On a lot of things,
on a lot of things,

26:23.934 --> 26:24.934
-you put your hands--
-But I have proof.

26:25.000 --> 26:26.967
-I have proof here.
-I'd like to see that.

26:27.033 --> 26:28.600
[Danny] That... was
gonna reach out to him.

26:28.667 --> 26:30.700
